# SkillSync

Sync AI coding skills (Claude Code, Cursor, Codex) across platforms.

**Stack**: Go 1.25.4, urfave/cli v3

## Architecture
```mermaid
graph LR
    CLI[cli/] --> Model[model/]
    CLI --> Parser[parser/]
    CLI --> Sync[sync/]
    Parser --> Model
    Sync --> Model
```

## Commands
- Build: `make build` | Test: `make test` | Audit: `make audit`
- Run: `./bin/skillsync --help`

## Issue Tracking
`bd ready` → `bd show <id>` → `bd close <id>`
